      <title>议员被停职后，苏纳克试图平息仇视伊斯兰教的争论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/sunak-faces-conservative-row-over-islamophobia-after-lee-anderson-suspended</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克(Rishi Sunak)正在努力遏制保守党内因伊斯兰恐惧症而发生的争吵，此前该党前副主席因声称工党伦敦市长萨迪克·汗(Sadiq Khan)受到“伊斯兰主义者”控制而被停职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/sunak-faces-conservative-row-over-islamophobia-after-lee-anderson-suspended</guid>
